headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Ubermacht Revolter
content: In your own mind, you’re something a little more important than an ordinary executive, and you need something that’s a little more than an ordinary luxury sedan. Something with more power, more presence, more room for a forward-facing machine gun mount. Now in showrooms across Los Santos, the Ubermacht Revolter is your definitive statement of fast, lethal intent and massive ego.
